The regional carriers and major trunk carriers of the
United States combine to form a complex pattern of
dependable airline transportation throughout our
nation. This "interline" dependence results in close
cooperation between all airlines ... and all designed
to serve you better.
At Delta Air Lines, the DELTAMATIC°reserva-
tions system can give instant confirmation not only
on Delta flights
but on 25 other airlines as well.
DELTAMATIC® keeps track of every seat on every
Delta flight and on virtually all other domestic air-
lines.
The same smooth harmony exists between Delta
and its interline partners in ticketing procedures,
baggage handling, etc. Around the clock this close
liaison between carriers is in evidence and your
connections are eased by it.
The next time you're "connecting" .. connect
to Delta and we'll show you what we mean!
DELTA
Delta serves major U.S. cities border-to-border
and coast-to-coast... thru the Gulf and Caribbean,
Delta's wings

of the western world
Perhaps the ideal vacation for you is a week or two
of fun on-the-go ... or maybe you prefer just a
pleasant respite from the workaday world.
Some
want vacation pleasure in a compact area ... others
like to wander through unexplored avenues of ad-
venture.
Whatever you want in a vacation, you'll find it
along the Jet routes of Delta. Make it magic Florida
for gaiety 'round the clock ... or relax with a bit
more elbow room in the tropic resort facilities of the
Bahamas and the Caribbean.
The fabulous west
coast of America is a tourist's delight and only a Jet
hop away from your door step. The fast action of Las
Vegas, the Vieux Carre of New Orleans, all the facili-
ties and flavors of a nation are yours to enjoy in a
thousand different ways...
. with as many different
budgets.
